metadata.name: Azuki x Gutter Punks
metadata.description: Azuki holders are invited to join the Gutter Punks in the biggest blockchain revolution since ERC-721A. Details on Twitter @GutterPunksNFT or visit https://mint.gutterpunks.co to mint now! We will be burning this NFT from wallets in a week unless it is sold, transferred or if you reach out letting us know you want to keep it.
